ormance ===\n{{hatnote|Each film is linked to the \"Box office\" section of its article.}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" | Film\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"3\" | Box office gross\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"2\" text=\"wrap\" class=unsortable | All-time ranking\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" | Budget\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" class=unsortable | {{nowrap|{{Abbr|Ref(s)|References}}}}\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | U.S. and Canada\n! scope=\"col\" | Other territories\n! scope=\"col\" | Worldwide\n! scope=\"col\" class=sortable | [[List of highest-grossing films in the United States and Canada#Franchises and film series not adjusted for inflation|U.S. and Canada]]\n! scope=\"col\" class=sortable | [[List of highest-grossing franchises and film series|Worldwide]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Man of Steel (film)#Box office|Man of Steel]]''\n| $291,045,518\n| $377,000,000\n| $668,045,518\n| 88\n| 120\n| $225 million\n| <ref name=\"MoSBOM\">{{cite web |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=superman2012.htm |title=Man of Steel (2013) |accessdate=February 7, 2018 |website=[[Box Office Mojo]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014020012/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=superman2012.htm |archive-date=October 14, 2013 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice#Box office|Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice]]''\n| $330,360,194\n| $543,274,725\n| $873,634,919\n| 58\n| 60\n| $250 million\n| <ref name=\"BvSBOM\">{{cite web |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=superman2015.htm |title=Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice (2016) |accessdate=February 7, 2018 |website=[[Box Office Mojo]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161216235108/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=superman2015.htm |archive-date=December 16, 2016 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Suicide Squad (film)#Box office|Suicide Squad]]''\n| $325,100,